Generate random NPIs

Source: R/experiments.R
random_npi_generator.Rd

Generate random NPIs

Usage

random_npi_generator(n)

Arguments

n

<integer> Number of NPIs to generate

Value

<character> vector of n NPIs

See also

Other mock: forager_data(), provider_data()

Examples

random_npi_generator(10)
#>  [1] "1280828733" "1609496447" "2862480287" "1101869342" "2071740308"
#>  [6] "1462809559" "1417990765" "1400683871" "1379290238" "1627305265"

x <- random_npi_generator(100)

x[collapse::whichv(purrr::map_lgl(x, is_valid_npi), TRUE)]
#> [1] "1501140465" "2642578613" "2405891906" "1086714288" "1333182750"
#> [6] "1778788897" "1210558510" "1135120602"
